            . I am an officer. The prisoner was brought to the watch-house by a street-keeper on the 14th of March; Mr. James Pearce, who keeps the Green Man public-house in New Bond-street, charged him with going up stairs into his house and taking this sheet off a bed in the third-floor room - he said he hoped he would forgive him.</p>
